  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/zipball/v3.28.0",
  "body": "> [!WARNING]\r\n> ### Ruby 3.2 no longer supports appsec on Lambda.\r\n\r\n```yml\r\n# AWS Commercial\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2-ARM:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3-ARM:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-4:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-4-ARM:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby4-0:28\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby4-0-ARM:28\r\n\r\n# AWS GovCloud\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2-ARM:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3-ARM:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-4:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-4-ARM:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby4-0:28\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Ruby4-0-ARM:28\r\n\r\nACCOUNT =\r\n002406178527 for us1 environment\r\n486696501492 for us2 environment\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Highlights\r\n- **Ruby 4.0 support** — adds new `Datadog-Ruby4-0` and `Datadog-Ruby4-0-ARM` layers. AWS Lambda added the `ruby4.0` managed runtime in April 2026; this release is the first to publish Datadog-instrumented layers for it. (#148)\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* feat: support Ruby 4.0 by @zarirhamza in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/148\r\n* bump minor version to 3.28.0 by @zarirhamza in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/149\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/compare/v3.27.0...v3.28.0",
